Prerequisites
=============

#. Configure the firewalls according to *Appendix A*.

#. Create machines according to *Appendix B - Inventory*.

#. Join the server ``{{ servers.issuing_ca.name }}`` to the domain ``{{ customer.domain }}``.

#. Share instructions and credentials for VPN access.

#. Create a local administrator account ``{{ accounts.local.user }}``.

#. Create an enterprise domain account ``{{ accounts.domain.user }}``.

#. Ensure that there is a network drive mapped to ``{{ servers.issuing_ca.name }}`` with at least 128 GB of free storage available for storing the CA logs and certificate database.

#. Ensure that the domain ``pki.{{ customer.domain }}`` points to ``{{ servers.repository.ip }}`` and can be resolved both internally and externally.